author: Huileng Tan
title: Coronavirus epicenter could 'possibly' shift back to Asia, says public health expert
description: The epicenter of the coronavirus outbreak is at risk of shifting constantly and "could possibly even shift back to East Asia," a public health expert said.
content:
The epicenter of the coronavirus outbreak is at risk of shifting constantly, posing challenges to public health systems, a health expert said on Thursday.
